narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would definitely recommend this course! It's a great way to fulfill a language requirement!

The course is great. Portuguese is a language in high depend if you are planning on going into business or are interested in the geopolitics of Latin America. The department is very small at Yale but it makes for a very tight knit community.
